title: Led Zeppelin - 1980.06.20 Brussels, Belgium
description:
Led Zeppelin - 1980.06.20 Brussels, Belgium   

LED ZEPPELIN
RAID OVER BRUSSELS
June 20, 1980
SOUNDBOARD

Source: 
Excellent soundboard recording.

Details: 
The recording is a very good balanced professional board tape.

Tracklist:

01. Train Kept A Rollin' 4:00
02. Nobody's Fault But Mine 6:22
03. Black Dog 5:59
04. In The Evening 8:30
05. The Rain Song (cut) 7:02
06. Hot Dog 4:45
07. All My Love 6:43
08. Trampled UnderFoot 8:49
09. Since I've Been Loving You 9:35
10. Achilles Last Stand 11:15
11. White Summer/Black Mountain Side 10:15
12. Kashmir 9:43
13. Stairway To Heaven 11:12
14. Rock And Roll 4:35
15. Whole Lotta Love (Boogie Chillun') 12:57

Comments: 
A really good show, although Jimmy destroys the sections of Achilles 
Last Stand. He delivers some great solos on Stairway To Heaven and 
Since I've Been Loving You. The rest of the band seems in fine shape, 
although Robert's lack of enthusiasm for Stairway is blatantly apparent
